This a modified US keyboard layout file. It adds German umlauts 
to the existing layout 'us(euro)'. Usage: 

 * Replace /usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/us with this one
 * Restart X, e.g. <Ctrl>-<Alt>-<Backspace> or logout/login
 * Go into the keyboard setting ans select this layout:

   "us(euro): English (US, with German umlauts and Euro via AltGr)"


See also:
 * http://hektor.umcs.lublin.pl/~mikosmul/computing/articles/custom-keyboard-layouts-xkb.html
 * http://www.charvolant.org/~doug/xkb/html/xkb.html
 * https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Howto%3A%20Custom%20keyboard%20layout%20definitions
